ArrayList----------->
It was introduced in jdk 1.2 version
ArrayList is not legacy class
ArrayList are non synchronized
ArrayList is not thread safe
Application speed is fast
ArrayList does not guarantte for data security
it does not provide any method to find capactiy


vector ---------->
It was introduced in jdk 1.0 version
vector is legacy class 
vector are synchronized 
vector is thread safe
Application speed is slow as compaerd to ArrayList
vector provide guarantte for data security
vector provide method (int capactiy()) to find the capacity of the vector